263@dataclass_json
264@dataclass
265class Details:
266    usd: float = 0
267    duration: float = 0
268    total_audio: float = 0
269    channels: int = 0
270    streams: int = 0
271    method: str = ""
272    models: List[str] = None
273    tags: Optional[List[str]] = field(
274        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
275    )
276    features: List[str] = None
277    config: Config = None
278    tier: Optional[str] = ""
279
280    def __getitem__(self, key):
281        _dict = self.to_dict()
282        if "models" in _dict:
283            _dict["models"] = [str(models) for models in _dict["models"]]
284        if "tags" in _dict:
285            _dict["tags"] = [str(tags) for tags in _dict["tags"]]
286        if "features" in _dict:
287            _dict["features"] = [str(features) for features in _dict["features"]]
288        if "config" in _dict:
289            _dict["config"] = Config.from_dict(_dict["config"])
290        return _dict[key]
291
292    def __setitem__(self, key, val):
293        self.__dict__[key] = val
294
295    def __str__(self) -> str:
296        return self.to_json(indent=4)

362@dataclass_json
363@dataclass
364class UsageRequest:
365    project_uuid: str = ""
366    request_id: str = ""
367    created: str = ""
368    path: str = ""
369    api_key_id: str = ""
370    response: Response = None
371    callback: Optional[Callback] = field(
372        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
373    )
374    accessor: Optional[str] = field(
375        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
376    )
377
378    def __getitem__(self, key):
379        _dict = self.to_dict()
380        if "response" in _dict:
381            _dict["response"] = Response.from_dict(_dict["response"])
382        if "callback" in _dict:
383            _dict["callback"] = Callback.from_dict(_dict["callback"])
384        return _dict[key]
385
386    def __setitem__(self, key, val):
387        self.__dict__[key] = val
388
389    def __str__(self) -> str:
390        return self.to_json(indent=4)

530    def __getitem__(self, key):
531        _dict = self.to_dict()
532        if "tags" in _dict:
533            _dict["tags"] = [str(tags) for tags in _dict["tags"]]
534        if "models" in _dict:
535            _dict["models"] = [
536                UsageModel.from_dict(models) for models in _dict["models"]
537            ]
538        if "processing_methods" in _dict:
539            _dict["processing_methods"] = [
540                str(processing_methods)
541                for processing_methods in _dict["processing_methods"]
542            ]
543        if "features" in _dict:
544            _dict["features"] = [str(features) for features in _dict["features"]]
545        if "languages" in _dict:
546            _dict["languages"] = [str(languages) for languages in _dict["languages"]]
547        return _dict[key]
548

550        self.__dict__[key] = val
551
552    def __str__(self) -> str:
553        return self.to_json(indent=4)

@classmethod
def schema( cls: Type[~A], *, infer_missing: bool = False, only=None, exclude=(), many: bool = False, context=None, load_only=(), dump_only=(), partial: bool = False, unknown=None) -> dataclasses_json.mm.SchemaF[~A]: 
 76    @classmethod
 77    def schema(cls: Type[A],
 78               *,
 79               infer_missing: bool = False,
 80               only=None,
 81               exclude=(),
 82               many: bool = False,
 83               context=None,
 84               load_only=(),
 85               dump_only=(),
 86               partial: bool = False,
 87               unknown=None) -> "SchemaType[A]":
 88        Schema = build_schema(cls, DataClassJsonMixin, infer_missing, partial)
 89
 90        if unknown is None:
 91            undefined_parameter_action = _undefined_parameter_action_safe(cls)
 92            if undefined_parameter_action is not None:
 93                # We can just make use of the same-named mm keywords
 94                unknown = undefined_parameter_action.name.lower()
 95
 96        return Schema(only=only,
 97                      exclude=exclude,
 98                      many=many,
 99                      context=context,
100                      load_only=load_only,
101                      dump_only=dump_only,
102                      partial=partial,
103                      unknown=unknown)
